ğŸ› ï¸ How It Works

FAQ Dictionary â€” All questions and answers are stored in a Python dictionary.
User Input â€” The user types a question in the chat box.
Matching Logic â€” The input is converted to lowercase and matched against the FAQ keys (exact match first, then partial match).
Response â€” The matching answer is displayed. If no match is found, a friendly fallback message is shown.


